::Liono::
Liono slowly finishes placing the last few space mines back into place "Void 
Hows the defense Grid?"

::Koj::

done over here she should fly."

::Lilly::
Lilly gentle trods up to Koj and inspects his work "Not too bad."
Lilly places her hand on Koj's shoulder gently.

::Void::
Void floating in air back at Cats Lair continues processing the defense 
progress as well as the work being done on the Cats Eye 1. She lifts her arm 
and waves it one time creating a view screen showing charts of their 
progress.  "The Ark defense grid is back at one-hundred percent the Cats Eye 
1 is fully function. The new changes you have made will insure the Arks 
safety."
